channel.title: I have made a forum 2 help players create servers
channel.description:
Need any help on creating your RS2 private server? Maybe so! well.. i have made a forum 2 help you make a server with tuts and other resources! 0wn3r tom has been helping me create the forum to 1, look better and 2, be more organised. he has also added a chat box 4 us and posted tuts and guides.
